 and every herb of the field before it was on the earth, and all the grass of the field before it sprang up, for God had not rained on the earth, and there was not a man to cultivate it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 6.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792  But there rose a fountain out of the earth, and watered the whole face of the earth. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 7.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
