\ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792  And God planted a garden eastward in Edem, and placed there the man whom he formed. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 9.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
