\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 10.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792  And a river proceeds out of Edem to water the garden, thence it divides itself into four heads. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 
