\ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792  And the Lord God took the man whom he had formed, and placed him in the garden of Delight, to cultivate and keep it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 16.}{\rtlch\fcs1 
