\cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792  My son, forget not my laws; but let thine heart keep my words: }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 2.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
 for length of existence, and years of life, and peace, shall they add to thee. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 3.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
 Let not mercy and truth forsake thee; but bind them about thy neck: }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 4.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
 so shalt thou find favor: and do thou provide things honest in the sight of the Lord, and of men. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 5.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
 Trust in God with all thine heart; and be not exalted in thine own wisdom. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 6.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
 In all thy ways acquaint thyself with her, that she may rightly direct thy paths. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 7.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
