 for whom the Lord loves, he rebukes, and scourges every son whom he receives. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 13.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792 
