 For length of existence and years of life are in her right hand; and in her left hand are wealth and glory: out of her mouth proceeds righteousness, and she carries law and mercy upon her tongue. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 
17.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f37\fs32\insrsid9401757\charrsid13377792  Her ways are good ways, and all her paths are peaceful. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\fs16\insrsid9401757 18.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
